1. To remove default margin and padding from html
    
    *{
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    }
    
2. By setting box-sizing to border-box we make size to include padding+border within it,
   by default it is content-box that doesn't include margin padding and border.
   Read-more:- https://www.w3schools.com/cssref/css3_pr_box-sizing.asp
